<div class="entry-content" itemprop="text">
<p>Bitcoin is the premier cryptocurrency but lately many want to get into other coins. So this site will help you make your entrance into the crypto space by explaining about bitcoins and other coins.</p>
<p>Please follow along with our blog as soon we will be publishing lots of new content.</p>
<h2>Bitcoin</h2>
<p>Bitcoin is the premier currency but today everyone just wants to buy trash like Bcash. Here is how to keep up with latest Bitcoin news and updates to follow:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://bitcoinmagazine.com/">Bitcoin Magazine</a></li>
<li><a href="https://coinjournal.net/">Coin Journal</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Most other sites do spam posts or paid posts so only use two sites above for your bitcoin. news.</p>
<p>If you wanna store your coins then we put up long guide on how to <a href="https://www.bitpremier.com/best-bitcoin-wallets">HODL bitcoins in a wallet</a>.</p>
<p>To get some coins check out some of the guides available on the web please stay tuned we still working on all the guides for BTC to buy. Try:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://bitcoin.org/en/buy">Bitcoin.org</a></li>
<li><a href="https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Buying_Bitcoins_(the_newbie_version)">Bitcoin Wiki</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.buybitcoinworldwide.com/en/buy-bitcoin-credit-debit-card/">Buy Bitcoins Worldwide</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.investopedia.com/tech/how-to-buy-bitcoin/">Investopedia</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>Litecoin</h2>
<p><a href="https://litecoin.org/">Litecoin</a> some say it is like silver to Bitcoin&#8217;s gold. But what is really meant by this saying? Well real gold is very big market but silver is small but still has value in other uses because it is easier to divide and use for small amounts so some think Litecoins will be used like this.</p>
<p>For Litecoin news and info check <a href="https://litecoin.org/">litecoin.org</a> and to buy LTCs try <a href="https://litecoin.info/Purchasing_litecoins">a guide</a>.</p>
<h2>Monero</h2>
<p>Monero is the best privacy coin DASH is not private and Zcash is not good because it has a developer reward that unfairly enriches the devs.</p>
<p>For Monero info<a href="https://getmonero.org/"> check the website</a> also follow creator of Monero <a href="https://twitter.com/fluffypony?lang=en">fluffypony on Twitter</a> and also check a <a href="https://getmonero.org/community/merchants/">guide to buy</a>.</p>
<h2>Ripple</h2>
<p>Ripple is a centralized coin but popular with the banks so we will throw up some info on it for you&#8230;..</p>
<p>First check out the <a href="https://ripple.com/">Ripple homepage</a> and there is good info on the coin it says:</p>
<blockquote><p>Ripple connects banks, payment providers, digital asset exchanges and corporates via RippleNet to provide one frictionless experience to send money globally.</p></blockquote>
<p><a href="https://ripple.com/xrp/buy-xrp/">Check a guide</a> for how to buy Ripple XRP our guide will be out soon.</p>
</div>
